cc.alcina.framework.gwt.persistence.client
Class LocalTransformPersistence

java.lang.Object
  cc.alcina.framework.gwt.persistence.client.LocalTransformPersistence
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientTransformManager.PersistableTransformListener, StateChangeListener, java.util.EventListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
DisabledTransformPersistence, LocalTransformPersistenceGwt
public abstract class LocalTransformPersistence
extends java.lang.Object
implements StateChangeListener, ClientTransformManager.PersistableTransformListener

Ordering of client transforms

Save:

  1. Inital object chunk: async
  2. Other (sync from remote, local transforms) - written synchronously

Load (offline):

  1. Initial object chunk (which may be out of order wrt db id)
  2. Other (sync from remote, local transforms) - ordered by id

This ensures that offline load is in the correct order

Author:
nick@alcina.cc
